  "title": "Optometrist / Optician (Full-Time / Part-Time) #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Optometrist / Optician (Full-Time / Part-Time)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide (Multiple Outlets Available)<br>\n <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Permanent / Contract / Part-Time<br>\n <strong>Salary Range:</strong> Up to $5,000/month (depending on experience)</p>\n<h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3>\n<p>We are seeking passionate and customer-oriented <em>Optometrists</em> and <em>Opticians</em> to join a retail-based optical team. You will provide professional eye care consultation, perform refraction tests, and deliver exceptional service to customers in a dynamic and fast-paced environment.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform vision tests, eye examinations, and refractions to determine customers’ prescriptions.</li>\n  <li>Advise customers on suitable eyewear options (spectacles, lenses, coatings, etc.) based on prescription and lifestyle.</li>\n  <li>Fit, adjust, and dispense optical products accurately.</li>\n  <li>Provide professional product and after-sales service to ensure high customer satisfaction.</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper documentation of prescriptions, eye test results, and sales transactions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure equipment, frames, and lenses are properly maintained and stored.</li>\n  <li>Support store operations including inventory management, visual display, and sales support when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Optometry / Opticianry or equivalent recognized qualification.</li>\n  <li>Fully registered with the Optometrists and Opticians Board (OOB), Singapore.</li>\n  <li>Internship experience is suffiencient , Training provided </li>\n  <li>Prior experience in retail optical or clinical settings will be an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Working Hours</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 or 5.5 days per week (rotating shifts, including weekends and PH)</li>\n  <li>Flexible working arrangements available</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p>\n<p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p>\n<p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Email : </strong><a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\"><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a></p>\n<p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
